title: Liger -- Saala Crossbreed
subTitle: A talented young MMA fighter trains hard to rise up the ranks. However, his goals are hindered when his lover is kidnapped.

title: International Khiladi: The Iron Man
subTitle: Amrita's parents get killed. Years later, she falls in love with Aditya only to learn that he was the one who was accused of her parents' murder.

title: Uvaa
subTitle: Five teenagers, who lead a carefree life, face challenges at their new convent school. Although their intentions are purely romantic, a horrifying event threatens to change their lives forever.

subTitle: Ruslaan, a terrorist's son, undergoes a major life change when an anti-terrorism officer adopts him. Determined to fix his bad reputation, Ruslaan becomes an intelligence agent.

title: Chithha
subTitle: Living a quiet life with his niece, Eeswaran manages to provide for her and nurtures her like a parent. However, his journey takes an insidous turn when she goes missing.

title: Buddy
subTitle: A terrible accident leaves Pallavi in a coma while her soul possesses the body of a teddy bear. With her organs in danger of being traded, she enlists the help of a pilot, Aditya.

subTitle: Nani, a middle-class boy with an eidetic memory, helps save his sister-in-law from a goon. Meanwhile, he also tries to convince his girlfriend's father to marry her off to him.

title: Saindhav
subTitle: A man with a traumatic past is compelled to encounter an crime boss so that he can rescue his daughter from a health problem.

subTitle: Surya, a young man with anger issues, channels his emotions on Saturdays, because of a promise to his deceased mother. However, things get complicated when he decides to confront a corrupt cop.

title: Taqdeerwala
subTitle: Yamraj and Chitragupt descend to Earth to look for the missing book of destiny. Soon, they find it in the possession of a man who refuses to part with it because it contains information of his mother's lifespan.

subTitle: Pehlwaan, a criminal, narrowly escapes a police encounter and uses a holy man's guise to hide. Though he soon amasses a large number of followers, he continues to carry out his illegal activities.

subTitle: Arivu desires a real love connection but ends up with Leela, who marries him out of family obligation. However, despite their differences, he tries his best to win her over.

subTitle: A driving instructor is tasked to take Shakeela, a young woman, to a landlord in Mussoorie. But soon, he finds out that her life is in danger and decides to be her saviour.

subTitle: An undercover police officer works in a school and tries to put an end to the criminal activities of two criminals who rule the area.

subTitle: Shiva's life takes an unexpected turn when a child mistakes him for her father. Upon learning the truth, Shiva vows to change his ways for the better.

title: Ragada
subTitle: Satya, a money-minded man, arrives in Hyderabad and starts working for a gangster, GK. However, he soon becomes the target of another gangster, Peddanna.

title: Yuvaraj

subTitle: Surya goes to Bangkok at his mother's request and changes his name to Siddhartha. He falls in love with Sahasra, but his mother asks him to marry the girl from his enemy's family.
